wikipedia_page.main: Martyn Rogers  (26 January 1960 – 29 February 1992) was an English footballer. His regular position was at full back. He was born in Nottingham.

response: Martyn Rogers (born 7 March 1955) is an English former professional footballer who played as a defender and now as a manager for Tiverton Town.

After being in charge of the club for over 1,000 games, Martyn Rogers tendered his resignation as manager of Tiverton Town on 18 May 2010, to take effect from 21 May. Chris Vinnicombe was appointed manager at a Ladysmead press conference on 7 June.
